claim_exhausted.body: You've collected the maximum amount. If you get new work and <whoIsEligible>become unemployed again</whoIsEligible>, you can reapply after this application expires on {{expirationDate, long_date}}.
claim_exhausted.footnote: Note: If you are enrolled in Additional Benefits during Training (ABT) you may still have funds. Try certifying online.
